            "title": "豪威登場高收16.22% 每手賬賺1700元",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">全球第3大數字圖像傳感器供應商豪威集團(00501)，H股今日掛牌，以全日高位121.8元收市，較招股價104.8元高16.22%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"豪威集成電路官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/12/OmniVision-Web.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"豪威集成電路官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/12/OmniVision-Web.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">豪威集成電路官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">該股全日穩企於招股價之上，開報108元即成全日低位，較招股價高3.05%；全日成交8.19億元。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">豪威集團A股(603501.SH)也借勢造好，收報133.55元人民幣，升1.54%。</p>\n</div>",
